name: Labyrinth of Doubt
description:
An undertaking in mixed media composition. Combining elements of rotoscoping, film, motion graphics, montage, 3D animation, photography, sound mixing, and oil on canvas. Breaking traditional rules of digital animation in order to create a new aesthetic. 1000 individually hand painted/drawn still frames. Stitched together. Interlaid with various forms of mixed media (scans of oil on canvas, digital photos, annotated MP4’s) 

- Original Beats
- Software used: Corel, Procreate, AfterEffects, Photoshop, Cinema 4D, & Ableton.
